                        <ol style="list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 16px;">
                            <li style="list-style-type: decimal; margin: 0px 0px 5px 20px; padding: 0px;">If your child can’t fill in the last word to a song phrase, give them a movement to imitate instead.</li>
